Day 09


    Operators:

    Arithmetic Operators (+-*/%)   --done
    Unary Operators (+,-,++,--)
    ShorthandOperators (=,+=,-=,*=,/=,%=)
    Relational Operators (>,<,<=,>=,==,!=)

    Unary Operators:
            	++: increase the value by 1.
            	-- : decreases the value by 1.

            	Post vs Pre:
                        		Pre : changes the value immediately
                        				++ a
                        				-- a

                        		post: changes the value in the second step.
                        				a ++
                        				a --

                 Assignments operator          Shorthand operator
                            x=x+y                              x+=y
                            x=x-y                              x-=y
                            x=x*y                              x*=y
                            x=x/y                              x/=y
                            x=x%y                              x%=y
                            x=y                                x=y


